(
h
) "Member" means a Member of the Authority and includes the Chairperson;
(
i
) "notification" means a notification published in the Official Gazette, and the
expressions "notified" and "notify" shall be construed accordingly;
(
j
) "prescribed" means prescribed by rules made by the Central Government
under this Act;
(
k
) "regulations" means the regulations made by the Authority under this Act.
